scene.message:
Drama President: Hey, Hirose.{nl}
You haven't shown up to{nl}
drama club practice at all{waitkey}{clearbox}lately. How can you skip the{nl}
rehearsals for "The Snow{nl}
Queen" when you play her?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone's working their{nl}
hardest, and you're fine{nl}
skipping out alone?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Do you have any sense of duty{nl}
as a member with a lead role?!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: That's right,{nl}
Kumi. Getting picked for{nl}
"Snow Queen" over the{waitkey}{clearbox}president, and then this?{nl}
Don't tell me it's gone{nl}
to your head?{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: But seriously,{nl}
it's a problem if you don't{nl}
come to practice a little.{waitkey}{clearbox}There's a limit to running{nl}
lines with a stand-in.{nl}
Kumi, what's your deal?{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: ...um...{nl}
...I-I have to... study...{nl}
...you see...{waitkey}{clearbox}...my grades dropped...{nl}
...and my... parents...{nl}
...said forget... club...{waitkey}...just study, they said...{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: Oh boy,{nl}
just like the parents of the{nl}
class's top crammer! C'mon.{waitkey}{clearbox}You were third in the whole{nl}
grade on the last test.{nl}
What's wrong with that?!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: What's that?!{nl}
Trying to be snide?!{nl}
Just 'cause you're a bit{waitkey}{clearbox}smart, don't get cocky!!{waitkey}{clearbox}If your precious studying{nl}
matters that much, then{nl}
just quit the club!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Frankly, you're a nuisance!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama President: Fine, then.{nl}
So that's why you haven't{nl}
been coming to club...{waitkey}{clearbox}Hirose... are you looking{nl}
down on me - no, on the{nl}
club itself?{waitkey}{clearbox}Do you understand how much{nl}
trouble you cause others by{nl}
not attending practice?{waitkey}{clearbox}While you fuss over your own{nl}
circumstances alone, do you{nl}
truly grasp how much{waitkey}{clearbox}trouble others suffer{nl}
because of it?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hirose... within this group{nl}
called the "drama club,"{nl}
what is your role right now?{waitkey}{clearbox}If you don't understand that,{nl}
then please leave{nl}
this club.{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: Yeah! Yeah!{nl}
The president's right!{nl}
Get out!{waitkey}{clearbox}You big-headed four-eyes!{nl}
A gloomy little nobody{nl}
like you{waitkey}{clearbox}is unpleasant just to{nl}
have around!{waitkey}{ret}

Drama Member: It's sad, but{nl}
the president's got a point,{nl}
y'know.{waitkey}{clearbox}Think hard, Kumi.{nl}
Studying or your youth -{nl}
which matters more to you...{waitkey}{clearbox}...or something.{waitkey}{ret}
